In [13]:
cmd.do('''
hide everything
set_bond stick_radius, 0.14, polymer
set sphere_scale, 0.25, polymer
set sphere_scale, 0.25, hydrogens
set label_size, 20
show sticks, name ca+c+n
sel nterm, resi 1
sel cterm, resi 153
label n. CA and i. 1, "(%s, %s)" % (resn, resi)
label n. CA and i. 153, "(%s, %s)" % (resn, resi)
show spheres, nterm
show sticks, nterm
show spheres, cterm
show sticks, cterm
sel aminogroup, name N and resi 1
h_add aminogroup
sel aminogroup, (name N or name H01 or name H02) and resi 1
label aminogroup, name
sel oxygen, name O and resi 153
label oxygen, name
set sphere_scale, 0.5, aminogroup
set sphere_scale, 0.5, oxygen
set label_color, magenta, aminogroup
set label_color, magenta, oxygen
orient
ray 800, 600
png img.png
''')
time.sleep(.1)
Image('img.png')
